          GOTO      KFMCSA10 IF NOT EQUAL
.
          MOVE      CCITEM,SCCITEM
          CALL      HFMCSA00
          MOVE      SCCITEM,CCITEM
.
          ENDSET    FMCSACC 
          APPEND    SP70,FMCSACC 
          RESET     FMCSACC 
.
